<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>실제<sp/>흐름</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>`UpdateModel()`이<sp/>logical/visual<sp/>model을<sp/>갱신</highlight></codeline>
