<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/>`AtlasRenderer::Render(Text::ViewInterface&amp;<sp/>view,<sp/>...)`<sp/>호출</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">즉,<sp/>renderer로<sp/>전달되는<sp/>최종<sp/>데이터는<sp/>`Text::ViewInterface`를<sp/>통해<sp/>나간다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">대표<sp/>데이터:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>glyphs</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>glyph<sp/>positions</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>default<sp/>color</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>glyph별<sp/>color<sp/>index</highlight></codeline>
