<codeline><highlight class="normal">어디부터<sp/>얼마만큼<sp/>다시<sp/>계산할지<sp/>기록한다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">주요<sp/>필드:</highlight></codeline>
