<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>TextVisualizer에<sp/>필요한<sp/>부분</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>직접<sp/>필요한<sp/>내용</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`mOperationsPending`<sp/>같은<sp/>dirty<sp/>비트마스크<sp/>개념</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`mTextUpdateInfo`처럼<sp/>update<sp/>범위를<sp/>좁히는<sp/>개념</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`UpdateModel()`<sp/>안의<sp/>prepare<sp/>단계</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>font<sp/>fallback</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>shaping</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>glyph<sp/>metrics</highlight></codeline>
